resource.title: Super Family Box
resource.shortDescription: 2 Medium Pizzas of your choice + 4 pcs. of Garlic Bread + Wedges + 1 Large Salad + 2 Dips + 2 Soft Drinks (500 ml)

bundleProductItems.title: Margherita
bundleProductItems.description: Go back to where it all began with the classic cheese and tomato base, topped with basil leaves.

bundleProductItems.title: Classic Pepperoni
bundleProductItems.description: One of our all-time specialties. A meaty feast of double pepperoni, mozzarella cheese and tomato sauce.

bundleProductItems.title: Spicy Tandoori Paneer
bundleProductItems.description: A vegetarian that isn’t shy about flavor. Enjoy spicy paneer with tandoori sauce, jalapenos, green peppers, mushrooms, and red & green chilis

bundleProductItems.title: Ultimate Cheese
bundleProductItems.description: Indulgent cream cheese scoops, on top of melting mozzarella in the base topped with cherry tomatoes & freshly sliced basil.

bundleProductItems.title: Very Veggie
bundleProductItems.description: Mushrooms, green peppers, fresh tomatoes, onions and black olives loaded on a tomato base and topped with melting mozzarella cheese.

bundleProductItems.title: Hot Stuff
bundleProductItems.description: Turn up the heat with juicy beef, sliced onions, tomatoes and spicy green chilies.

bundleProductItems.title: Super Supreme
bundleProductItems.description: Our famous combination of beef pepperoni, juicy beef, mushrooms, green peppers, onions, black olives and melting mozzarella cheese.

bundleProductItems.title: Mediterranean Shrimp Lovers
bundleProductItems.description: Shrimp, fresh tomatoes, green peppers, black olives and freshly chopped garlic along with tomato sauce and topped with cheese.

bundleProductItems.title: Seafood Island
bundleProductItems.description: The ultimate seafood pizza! Generously topped with a sea of shrimps, calamari and green peppers

bundleProductItems.title: Tropical Hawaiian
bundleProductItems.description: Complete with roasted turkey ham, mozzarella cheese and juicy pineapples.

bundleProductItems.title: Cheeky Chicken
bundleProductItems.description: Dig in to our succulent pieces of grilled chicken, green peppers, onions and fresh tomatoes.

bundleProductItems.title: Chicken BBQ
bundleProductItems.description: Classic grilled chicken draped in a mouthwatering BBQ sauce along with mozzarella cheese,  sliced red onions, garnised with basil.

bundleProductItems.title: Chicken Fajita
bundleProductItems.description: Sliced pieces of chicken fajita, onions, diced tomatoes, on a rich tomato base topped with spring onions and melted mozzarella.

bundleProductItems.title: Chicken Shawerma
bundleProductItems.description: Grilled chicken on garlic sauce, topped with mozzarella, sliced pickles, chopped onions, diced tomatoes and parsley.

bundleProductItems.title: Chicken Super Supreme
bundleProductItems.description: The ultimate mix of chicken pepperoni and juicy grilled chicken strips together with mushrooms, red onions, green peppers, olives and melting mozzarella cheese

bundleProductItems.title: Mexicana Chicken
bundleProductItems.description: Mexi-can you feel it? A grilled chicken pizza with roquito salsa, sweet corn, chopped jalapenos, and a drizzle of sour cream

bundleProductItems.title: Red Pepper Chicken
bundleProductItems.description: Don’t be chicken. Try this spicy chicken pizza with Extreme Spicy Sauce, roasted red pepper, chopped jalapenos, and a sweet chili sprinkle

bundleProductItems.title: Spicy Chicken Ranch
bundleProductItems.description: Grilled chicken, fresh tomatoes, mushrooms and green Jalapeño peppers with a drizzle of thick Peri Peri sauce.
